.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-CREATE-ACCOUNT" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-create-account \- create a named account within a wallet
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-create-account
.I wallet_name account_name
.SH DESCRIPTION
Inserts a named account into the wallet's accounts table.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"status":"created","wallet":"<name>","account":"<account>"}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-info (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-ledger-add (1)
